{"nodes": [{"id": "draft6_0_research_papers_phase9_slow_coordination", "label": "Slow coordination (story file)", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\papers\\phase9\\slow-coordination.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": null}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_papers_phase9_slow_coordination_momentum_encoder", "label": "EMA / momentum encoder (Mean Teacher, MoCo, BYOL, DINO)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\papers\\phase9\\slow-coordination.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "A slow EMA teacher buys STABILITY (smoother targets), the only thing the SCFF base needs from anything downstream; it matters most at the LATE layers = our drift-slowdown flip, doubly grounded."}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_papers_phase9_slow_coordination_stop_gradient", "label": "Stop-gradient (read-only relation)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\papers\\phase9\\slow-coordination.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Names GD-reads-SCFF-never-writes; necessary but not sufficient \u2014 it blocks the backward leak, but boosting-chain still poisoned the base through the FORWARD leak of the residual stream."}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_papers_phase9_slow_coordination_lookahead", "label": "Lookahead slow/fast weights", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "draft6.0\\research\\papers\\phase9\\slow-coordination.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Formalizes slow/fast weights = a fast online readout tracking drift + a slow sleep-consolidated readout; the two-timescale split survives boosting's death, living inside the readout."}, {"id": "draft6_0_research_papers_phase9_slow_coordination_boos